Welcome to "aim_carnage_ll_v3"
Map created By El_Mexicano & el_cubano


This is an "aim" map , with 24 slots in each team for a total of 48 slots 
Very very fun map , the aim ?????: the two teams are separeted by a wall, you begin onyl with the cut , there is a countdown from ten to 0 will permit you to take any weapon , the harder
way you'll go for the weapon, the better will be the weapon !!!! after ten secondes the wall explode and the team are face to face and the carnage can begin !!!!!!!!

Just have a look at the video to see the FUN gameplay
i included the .RES file which allow you to put it on your serv easier
